data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. New Year - New Townhome- Currently Vacant-     *Now offering a SELLER CREDIT of $3,000 towards the buyers closing costs, prepaids or a rate buy down.     Back On The Market - Buyer's financing fell through. All inpsections were completed and property is priced below apprasied value for a quick sale.     This is a charming townhome in Riverview, Florida in a wonderful community with so much to do! This property is a two-level townhome, with 1280 sq.ft. offering an open layout that seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, perfect for everyday living and hosting friends.     Enjoy two spacious bedrooms with ample closet space and two full bathrooms upstairs, offering privacy. The primary bathroom offers a large garden tub. A convenient half bath downstairs is easily accessible for guests. The in-unit washer and dryer upstairs make laundry hassle-free.    The community features a refreshing pool, parks, boardwalks, and a playground. With close proximity to schools, shops, dining, and recreational spots, this home is ideal for all buyers.
